    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = (wp.cos((tmp + 0.31 * tmp + 0.34)) / ((tmp + 0.78 / v1 + 0.74) + (tmp + 0.24 / v1 + 0.50)))
    v2 = (wp.exp(0.46) / ((v2 + 0.00 + tmp + 0.49) + (v0 + 0.91 - v0 + 0.44)))
    v1 = tmp
    v0 = (wp.exp(wp.sin(v1 + 0.82)) * 0.39)
    v0 = ((wp.sin(v1 + 0.54) * wp.sin(v1 + 0.78)) + tmp)
    v1 = wp.cos((0.04 / wp.cos(v2 + 0.55)))
    tmp = wp.sin(wp.cos((v2 + 0.05 / tmp + 0.78)))
    v0 = ((v0 + 0.61) * wp.exp(0.03))
    data[tid] = v0
